thread.title: Jon-Paul Rutan

author: Jon-Paul Rutan
title: Jon-Paul Rutan
text: The title above says it all. I ordered woven patches and coins. Great product. The quality I received was above my expectations. Professional service. Their staff was great to work with. Fair price. Because their prices were so good, I was worried about the quality and the service that I was going to receive. When I got the products I realized that all my fears were unfounded. Give them a chance at your business, you won't regret it.
